{"tid":1665913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[日本戰線] 形象工程最後機會！","createTime":"2019-10-20T17:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T18:07:48.000Z","uid":249705,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16527de8a16e38181254e982f923cf260843ba68","tid":1665913,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:53:33.000Z","msg":"之前講過<br />\n作為香港人<br />\n喺人道定政治立場<br />\n都應該捐款幫日本重建<br />\n<br />\n香港示威者捐款 援助日本風災<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1653828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1653828</a><br />\n<blockquote>日本而家經歷60年一遇嘅風災<br />\n43個縣入面 有36個縣受影響<br />\n關東東北地區嚴重受創<br />\n超過1000萬人要避難<br />\n<br />\n香港人(抗爭者)一定要籌錢幫手<br />\n<br />\n日本係香港需要重點拉攏既盟友<br />\n更加係美國喺太平洋地區克制中國嘅重地<br />\n係朋友嘅朋友 敵人嘅敵人<br />\n籌款幫手重建 打好關係絕對有益無害<br />\n<br />\n另外外國議員記者多次提醒<br />\n依家暴力場面比例較多<br />\n形象工程需要跟上升級速度<br />\n有咩Juicy得過示威者籌錢賑災?<br />\n<br />\n6月嗰陣<br />\n日本首相已經專登喺G20講起香港<br />\n當面向習近平施壓<br />\n單係呢個舉動已經值得籌錢幫手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早前大J搞咗眾籌<br />\n同時有周庭幫手推廣<br />\n暫時一個星期之內籌到106萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drnhx4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdrnhx4M.jpg&h=15c836c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ur8TQRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUr8TQRv.jpg&h=96b12a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨番最後幾個鐘<br />\n如果有心想幫日本既手足<br />\n可以趁今次機會一齊捐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n一齊以<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span>名義捐<br />\n比分開捐嘅意義大</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e6%8f%b4%e5%8a%a9%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e5%8f%97%e5%8f%b0%e9%a2%a8%e3%80%8c%e6%b5%b7%e8%b2%9d%e6%80%9d%e3%80%8d%e4%be%b5%e8%a5%b2%e5%be%8c%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e5%bb%ba/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e6%258f%25b4%25e5%258a%25a9%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%259c%25ac%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%258f%25b0%25e9%25a2%25a8%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e8%25b2%259d%25e6%2580%259d%25e3%2580%258d%25e4%25be%25b5%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e5%25be%258c%25e7%259a%2584%25e9%2587%258d%25e5%25bb%25ba%2F&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=bf10c993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e6%8f%b4%e5%8a%a9%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e5%8f%97%e5%8f%b0%e9%a2%a8%e3%80%8c%e6%b5%b7%e8%b2%9d%e6%80%9d%e3%80%8d%e4%be%b5%e8%a5%b2%e5%be%8c%e7%9a%84%e9%87%8d%e5%bb%ba/</a>"},{"pid":"8109e467407a7681f07dfa00f7c475379e20b94a","tid":1665913,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:54:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af99234a76a1a5181440f39a5a788c96a6f89174","tid":1665913,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"國際戰線手足需要支援！"},{"pid":"903e5a8b77294c0231ba1a40fe79b660efad6e3e","tid":1665913,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4X3P8Gr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4X3P8Gr.jpg&h=80e69854&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8244c3b0b675f4524a68ee1bec51e1be741c683e","tid":1665913,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bukGfmB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbukGfmB.jpg&h=230823f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKcmfmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKcmfmC.jpg&h=0c634682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AH5G1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AH5G1D.